#

Caprese Toast

15 min
$5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

QuickHealthyBrunch

Description

A fresh and vibrant toast topped with juicy tomatoes, creamy mozzarella, and fragrant basil, drizzled with balsamic glaze for an extra touch of flavor.

Ingredients

  • sourdough bread: 2 slices
  • fresh mozzarella cheese: 100 grams
  • ripe tomatoes: 1 medium
  • fresh basil leaves: a handful
  • balsamic glaze: to drizzle
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
